videos.description: Victoria Vivians is left wide-open and drills an open 3-pointer, much to the bench's delight.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Vivians drains trey

videos.description: Roshunda Johnson dishes it to an open Blair Schaefer who drains a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Johnson finds Schaefer for 3

videos.description: Morgan Williams finds an open lane and drives to the basket uncontested for a layup.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Williams gets to rim for layup

videos.description: No. 2 Mississippi State remains undefeated with a 76-55 win over No. 17 Texas A&M behind Victoria Vivians 26 points, including five 3-pointers.
